<!-- Campaign event template USSR dispatch - formatting taken from real world examples -->
<Page
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
  xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
  xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
  xmlns:local="clr-namespace:SeapowerUI"
  mc:Ignorable="d"
  d:DesignWidth="1920"
  d:DesignHeight="1080">
  <Viewbox>
    <Border HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="900" Height="1272" Padding="45" TextElement.FontFamily="Courier New" TextElement.Foreground="Black" TextElement.FontSize="16">
		<Border.Effect>
			<DropShadowEffect />
		</Border.Effect>
		
		<Border.Background>
			<ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding Assets[bkg_paper]}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
		</Border.Background>
		
        <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical">

		<Grid
		  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
		  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml" >
		<Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
		</Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
				<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
				<ColumnDefinition Width="3*"/>
				<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
			</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			
			<TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Grid.Column="0" Text="# 389/PR/52" Margin="0" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Left"/>
			<TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="0" Text="10.07.85 r." Margin="0" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Left"/>
			<TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Grid.Column="1" Text="" Margin="40,0,40,0" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Center"/>
			<TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Grid.Column="2" Text="Cовершенно cекретно" Margin="0" TextDecorations="Underline" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Right"/>
			<TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="2" Text="Экз. № 1" Margin="0" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Center"/>
		</Grid>

				<TextBlock Text="DIRECTIVE No.028/85" Margin="0" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Left"/>
				<Rectangle HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" Height="1" Fill="Black" Margin="0,0,0,1"/>
				<Rectangle HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" Height="1" Fill="Black" Margin="0,0,0,10"/>

			<Grid
			  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
			  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
			<Grid.RowDefinitions>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="10"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
					<RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
				</Grid.RowDefinitions>
				<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
					<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
					<ColumnDefinition Width="10"/>
					<ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
					<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
				</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="FROM:"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="Commander, Red Banner Northern Fleet"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="TO:"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="Commander, Strike Group MOLNIYA"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="COPY:"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="GHQ 8th Operational Squadron, Red Banner Pacific Fleet"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="6" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="SUBJECT:"/>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="6" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Text="Further Operations in Indian Ocean"/>

				<TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" TextWrapping="Wrap" FontWeight="Bold">
					<LineBreak/>
					Command acknowledges receipt of your post-engagement and resupply report dated 09 JUL after combat action in Crozet Islands. Fuel, ammunition, and aviation stores are assessed as sufficient to enable continued maneuver and combat operations.
					<LineBreak/>
					<LineBreak/>
					GHQ extends congratulations to the officers and crews of Strike Group Molniya. Operational losses inflicted on REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA forces have compelled their government to enter negotiations and declare neutrality in the conflict. Remaining opposition in this theater is now assessed to be limited to American units.
					<LineBreak/>
					<LineBreak/>
					However, our compartmented sources within America have passed warning that the USS Enterprise carrier group is being rerouted from the Arabian Sea to find and destroy you. We assess that continued engagement against this force would risk unacceptable personnel losses without corresponding operational benefit.
					<LineBreak/>
					<LineBreak/>
					You are therefore directed to initiate transit north toward neutral INDIAN waters, avoiding established shipping areas and predictable patrol lanes. Command has brokered a deal with Government of India to shelter your force at their fleet base in COCHIN. This arrangement will preserve Strike Group Molniya for potential future operations and compel U.S. forces to remain committed in theater.
					<LineBreak/>
					<LineBreak/>
					Further operational guidance will be transmitted as possible. If targets of opportunity present themselves, we will pass to you for execution. Good luck, Comrades.
					<LineBreak/>
				</TextBlock>
				<TextBlock Grid.Row="8" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" TextWrapping="Wrap" FontWeight="Bold">
					END OF DIRECTIVE
					<LineBreak/>
					/s/ Kapitanets
					<LineBreak/>
					<LineBreak/>
					Cовершенно cекретно
					<LineBreak/>
					После прочтения — уничтожить
				</TextBlock>
			</Grid>
        </StackPanel>
    </Border>
</Viewbox>
</Page>